326
00:27:38,165 --> 00:27:42,624
<i>According to records, you were incarcerated
at the time of the Cooper hijacking.</i>

327
00:27:42,708 --> 00:27:47,751
My father and I share more
than just a weakness for easy money.

328
00:27:47,834 --> 00:27:49,418
