369
00:33:41,288 --> 00:33:43,747
Brad. Yours?

370
00:33:43,831 --> 00:33:47,665
- Jasmine.
- Come on, your real name.

371
00:33:49,749 --> 00:33:53,208
- It's Nika.
- Nika.

372
00:33:53,291 --> 00:33:56,042
That's a pretty name.

373
00:33:56,125 --> 00:33:58,251
Tell me, Nika...

374
00:33:59,043 --> 00:34:02,001
How's your husband feel
about you working here?

375
00:34:02,085 --> 00:34:04,002
I'm not married.

376
00:34:04,086 --> 00:34:06,962
I hope you're lying for the sake of titillation.

377
00:34:07,045 --> 00:34:13,296
Otherwise, your little visit to Fox River this
