a little more about your husband.

382
00:34:31,092 --> 00:34:33,676
- Well, he's a very good man.
- I'm sure he is.

383
00:34:33,759 --> 00:34:37,301
But even good men do bad things.

384
00:34:39,344 --> 00:34:43,136
Your accent. You're from, don't tell me...

385
00:34:43,220 --> 00:34:45,428
- Budapest, right?
- Prague.

386
00:34:45,512 --> 00:34:49,846
Prague. How recently did you come over?

387
00:34:49,930 --> 00:34:53,889
Only a couple months, I bet.
You like it here in America?

388
00:34:53,973 --> 00:34:57,515
