403
00:36:31,286 --> 00:36:35,162
<i>Dorothy Andrews Elston Kabis.</i>

404
00:36:35,246 --> 00:36:41,039
United States treasurer, 1971.
The year of the DB Cooper hijacking.

405
00:36:43,873 --> 00:36:47,916
Dl192589.

406
00:36:48,000 --> 00:36:53,251
The first number in the series of bills
used in the ransom drop.

407
00:36:53,959 --> 00:36:59,085
<i>- Thanks for the history lesson.
- All it proves is you did the research.</i>

408
00:36:59,168 --> 00:37:01,253
Same as me.

409
00:37:40,512 --> 00:37:43,387
So you're married?

410
00:37:43,470 --> 00:37:46,638
Uh, well...
Not in the traditional sense of the word.

411
00:37:46,722 --> 00:37:51,931
Michael, we're both adults.
Put your cards on the table.

412
00:37:53,806 --> 00:37:55,890
OK. I'll go first.

413
00:37:57,391 --> 00:37:58,391
Um...

414
00:37:59,015 --> 00:38:04,101
