And please let me finish.

418
00:38:18,812 --> 00:38:22,896
I'm not ajealous woman.
But I'm a careful one.

419
00:38:22,980 --> 00:38:25,981
And for some reason,
when I'm around you I'm not careful.

420
00:38:26,064 --> 00:38:29,189
- You don't have to be.
- Yes, I do.

421
00:38:29,273 --> 00:38:35,066
There's so many questions surrounding you,
Michael. There are way too many.

422
00:38:35,150 --> 00:38:37,942
So here's the deal. Um...

423
00:38:38,025 --> 00:38:43,651
From now on, your shots, medical concerns,
they're all fine, as long as it's doctorlpatient.

424
00:38:43,734 --> 00:38:49,611
But personal questions and favours of any
kind are no longer a part of our relationship.

425
00:38:51,820 --> 00:38:54,737
The questions you have about me...

426
00:38:56,113 --> 00:38:58,989
There are answers.

427
00:39:08,116 --> 00:39:09,699
Quinn.

428
00:39:09,782 --> 00:39:12,908
Hey, I was getting worried.
You guys get lost?

429
00:39:12,992 --> 00:39:16,701
We called you again to pinpoint your signal,
but you never picked up.

430
00:39:16,784 --> 00:39:19,493
Battery went dead on the damn cellphone.

431
00:39:19,577 --> 00:39:22,536
So, uh... How'd it go?

432
00:39:22,619 --> 00:39:25,036
Well, I got a broken leg down here.

433
00:39:25,120 --> 00:39:28,453
Listen, you know,
I think maybe we got off on the wrong foot.

434
00:39:28,537 --> 00:39:33,080
You got bosses, I got bosses, but at the end
of the day we're all on the same team.

435
00:39:33,164 --> 00:39:35,497
Right? Just trying to tie up loose ends.

436
00:39:35,581 --> 00:39:39,081
- I could not agree more.
- Yeah. So can you guys get a rope,

437
00:39:39,164 --> 00:39:41,456
or a ladder, or something?

438
00:39:46,041 --> 00:39:48,792
What the hell's that?

439
00:39:48,876 --> 00:39:51,126
Hey, hey! Hey!

440
00:39:51,209 --> 00:39:55,002
- Just tying up some loose ends.
- You son of a... Hey!

441
00:39:55,085 --> 00:39:57,836
Don't do this. Don't do this!

442
00:39:59,586 --> 00:40:02,753
<i>- Come on, please.
- My leg is broken. I can't stand.</i>

443
00:40:02,837 --> 00:40:05,337
You can'tjust leave him down there.
He'll die.

444
00:40:05,421 --> 00:40:09,297
He's the only one who knows
we don't have the Burrows kid.

445
00:40:09,380 --> 00:40:12,172
<i>- The only one.
- I got a family!</i>

446
00:40:16,506 --> 00:40:20,258
There's room for you down there too, Danny.

447
00:40:22,049 --> 00:40:25,758
<i>- Don't leave me like this.
- Don't leave me. Please!</i>

448
00:40:25,842 --> 00:40:27,926
Please!

449
00:40:32,844 --> 00:40:36,886
Coming back to PI today?
It's getting kind of testy in there, you know.

450
00:40:36,970 --> 00:40:39,053
<i>Yeah.</i>

451
00:40:40,804 --> 00:40:43,305
I just needed to find something out.

452
00:40:43,388 --> 00:40:46,014
- What the hell's that?
- Listen.

453
00:40:52,432 --> 00:40:55,182
- Am I supposed to be hearing something?
- Shh.

454
00:40:55,266 --> 00:40:57,474
Just hold on.

455
00:41:12,978 --> 00:41:14,270
There.

456
00:41:14,353 --> 00:41:17,771
What? We sat around here
for 20 minutes waiting to hear that?

457
00:41:17,855 --> 00:41:20,188
18 minutes, actually.

458
00:41:20,272 --> 00:41:22,105
And yes.

459
00:41:23,314 --> 00:41:25,815
- What was it?
- Keys.

460
00:41:25,897 --> 00:41:28,107
The guards' keys.

461
00:41:28,190 --> 00:41:30,316
18 minutes between each time

462
00:41:30,399 --> 00:41:33,774
the guards pass the infirmary windows
on their rounds at night.

463
00:41:33,858 --> 00:41:37,817
Cons aren't allowed out after hours.
Only way I could find out the timing.

464
00:41:37,900 --> 00:41:40,901
- What does that mean?
- It means...

465
00:41:41,985 --> 00:41:44,444
Four days from now,
on the night of the escape,

466
00:41:44,527 --> 00:41:47,403
we'll have 18 minutes
to get the bars off the window

467
00:41:47,486 --> 00:41:51,237
and for all seven of us
to get across the wire and over the wall.

468
00:41:51,321 --> 00:41:53,821
- Is that doable?
- Of course.

469
00:42:08,241 --> 00:42:11,492
- What's up?
- Nothing.

470
00:42:11,576 --> 00:42:14,325
<i>- Hey, I know that look. What's up?</i>

471
00:42:14,409 --> 00:42:17,160
I hit it. I hit it!

