<i>The pipe!</i>

473
00:42:21,619 --> 00:42:24,412
<i>Guys, guys.</i>

474
00:42:24,495 --> 00:42:26,412
All right, all right.

475
00:42:29,663 --> 00:42:33,289
- Come on, Michael. Talk to me.
- You want the good news or the bad news?

476
00:42:33,372 --> 00:42:36,664
- The good.
- Westmoreland and his money are in.

477
00:42:37,498 --> 00:42:40,249
- What's the bad?
- I've done the math.

478
00:42:40,332 --> 00:42:44,833
It'll take at least five minutes for us to get
the bars off the window in the infirmary,

479
00:42:44,916 --> 00:42:47,876
two minutes each
to get across the wire and over the wall.

480
00:42:47,959 --> 00:42:50,626
- So?
- We've only got 18 minutes.

481
00:42:52,002 --> 00:42:54,753
We've got too many people.

482
00:42:57,128 --> 00:43:00,211
One of 'em has to go.

